### Workspace IDE 聚合 API 测试

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000
@tenantId = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001
@username = admin
@password = P@ssw0rd!
@workspaceId = 1001
@targetWorkspaceId = 1002
@folderId = 2001

### 登录
# @name login
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/token
Content-Type: application/json
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

{
  "username": "{{username}}",
  "password": "{{password}}"
}

###
@accessToken = {{login.response.body.$.data.accessToken}}

### 获取 CSRF Token
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

###

### 获取工作空间摘要
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/workspace-ide/summary
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### 获取 Dashboard 统计卡片
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/workspace-ide/dashboard-stats
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### 获取统一资源列表（支持 folderId/status/workspaceId 过滤）
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/workspace-ide/resources?pageIndex=1&pageSize=24&keyword=&resourceType=app&favoriteOnly=false&folderId={{folderId}}&status=draft&workspaceId={{workspaceId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### 查询资源被引用关系（示例：数据库）
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/workspace-ide/resources/database/1/references
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### 获取发布中心聚合列表
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/workspace-ide/publish-center/items?resourceType=
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### 创建 AI 应用并自动生成默认工作流
# @name createWorkspaceApp
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/workspace-ide/apps
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Coze 工作空间应用",
  "description": "通过工作空间 IDE 一键创建",
  "icon": "bot"
}

###
@workspaceAppId = {{createWorkspaceApp.response.body.$.data.appId}}
@workspaceWorkflowId = {{createWorkspaceApp.response.body.$.data.workflowId}}

### 标记收藏
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/workspace-ide/favorites/app/{{workspaceAppId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "isFavorite": true
}

### 记录最近编辑
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/workspace-ide/activities
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "resourceType": "app",
  "resourceId": {{workspaceAppId}},
  "resourceTitle": "Coze 工作空间应用",
  "entryRoute": "/work_flow/{{workspaceWorkflowId}}/editor"
}

### 创建副本（当前空间）
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/workspace-ide/resources/app/{{workspaceAppId}}/duplicate
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "workspaceId": "{{workspaceId}}",
  "folderId": "{{folderId}}"
}

### 迁移到其它空间（当前空间移除）
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/workspace-ide/resources/app/{{workspaceAppId}}/migrate
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sourceWorkspaceId": "{{workspaceId}}",
  "targetWorkspaceId": "{{targetWorkspaceId}}"
}

### 复制到其它空间（当前空间保留）
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/workspace-ide/resources/app/{{workspaceAppId}}/copy-to-workspace
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sourceWorkspaceId": "{{workspaceId}}",
  "targetWorkspaceId": "{{targetWorkspaceId}}"
}

### 永久删除资源
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/workspace-ide/resources/app/{{workspaceAppId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}
